<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="conservation status">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Conservation status in Cameroon.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. Cusset, Adansonia ser., 2, 14 (2): 275" authorityYear="1974" baseAuthorityName="Engl." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Podostemaceae" genus="Ledermanniella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Ledermanniella schlechteri" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="schlechteri">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Ledermanniella schlechteri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is listed on http://www.iucnredlist.org as Vulnerable, globally (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.2305/iucn.uk.2010-3.rlts.t185208a8366931.en" author="Ghogue, J-P" journalOrPublisher="Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B38" refString="Ghogue, J-P, 2010j. Ledermanniellaschlechteri. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2010: e.T185208A8366931. https://doi.org/10.2305/iucn.uk.2010-3.rlts.t185208a8366931.en" title="Ledermanniellaschlechteri. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2010: e. T 185208 A 8366931." url="https://doi.org/10.2305/iucn.uk.2010-3.rlts.t185208a8366931.en" year="2010 j">Ghogue 2010j</bibRefCitation>
). The taxon is known from two localities. The extent of occurrence is less than 100 km2, and the area of occupancy is about 8 km2. The proposed dam at Edea waterfall will further deteriorate the quality of the habitat of the species at that locality. Base on this threat and the number of localities where the species is currently found, 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="L." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="L. schlechteri" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="schlechteri">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">L. schlechteri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here reassessed as Endangered. IUCN Red List Category: 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Endangered ENB1+2ab (iii).</emphasis>
</paragraph>
